WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:01.820
Are un miros bun.

00:02.980 --> 00:04.660
Poftim!

00:06.200 --> 00:07.420
Cum este?

00:08.700 --> 00:11.540
Se pare că nu-ți c-am place, nu?

00:11.980 --> 00:12.820
Prea amar?

00:12.820 --> 00:14.760
Ce-ar fi dacă ai pune un pic de zahăr?

00:14.760 --> 00:18.720
Well, how about if you add some milk? It might take away the bitterness.

00:19.280 --> 00:21.100
Or vrei să-ți dau altceva?

00:21.920 --> 00:23.320
Nu-mi place laptele.

00:23.720 --> 00:31.440
Ah, scuze, Nu știam.. Ce-ar fi dacă ți-aș da un suculeț?

00:34.120 --> 00:35.020
Scuze...

00:36.180 --> 00:41.040
I probably couldn’t have had tea at your age, either.

00:43.040 --> 00:46.700
Am zis că-s multe feluri de ceaiuri, nu?

00:46.700 --> 00:48.700
Dacă nu-mi place, nu-mi place!

00:49.280 --> 00:57.140
Of course, that doesn’t mean I can’t drink it, but I have my own preferences as to what kinds of flavors I like in tea.

00:59.140 --> 01:00.800
Ce-ți place, Lain?

01:01.800 --> 01:03.700
De ce nu-ți place laptele?

01:04.340 --> 01:06.040
Mă deranjează la stomac.

01:06.280 --> 01:11.250
Haha, să fiu sincer, și eu am avut aceeași problemă, când eram copilă.

01:11.920 --> 01:17.840
Especially when the school lunch included milk. I can drink milk now, though.

01:17.840 --> 01:19.840
Nu pot să-l beau, dar chiar îmi place laptele...

01:20.180 --> 01:23.880
How about this kind of milk? Would that be all right?

01:23.880 --> 01:25.660
Cum se cheamă?

01:25.660 --> 01:30.780
I forget what it’s called, but it’s milk that doesn’t upset your stomach.

01:31.410 --> 01:34.880
It's for kids like you, Lain, who are like me as a kid and can’t drink milk.

01:35.520 --> 01:38.720
Daca vorbești cu mama ta, sunt sigură că o să se intereseze.
